OL,3,CMum's warning over super-strength drug
OL,4,Cwhich killed her son
OL,6,FA mum whose son died of an overdose
OL,7,Fsays she is "astounded" hardly anyone
OL,8,Fknows about the super-strength drugs
OL,9,Fwhich killed him.
OL,11,FYoung musician Dylan Rocha, from
OL,12,FSouthampton, was 21 when he took
OL,13,Fheroin which was laced with a nitazene
OL,14,F- a synthetic opioid which can be
OL,15,Fdeadly in tiny doses.
OL,17,FHe is thought to be the first person
OL,18,Fin the UK to have died from taking
OL,19,Fnitazenes, which can be up to 500
OL,20,Ftimes stronger than heroin.
