OL,6,FHis mum Claire said: "I got a phone
OL,7,Fcall from his girlfriend saying that
OL,8,Fthe paramedics were with Dylan and
OL,9,Fhe's taken something and she said it
OL,10,Fdoesn't look good.
OL,12,F"And when I got there the paramedic
OL,13,Fcame out and he said to me I'm sorry
OL,14,Fbut we did everything we could,
OL,15,FDylan's gone.
OL,17,F"And just the shock of that...it's
OL,18,Fbewildering. You still can't get over
OL,19,Fit to this day really. That it
OL,20,Fhappened so quickly in such a short
OL,21,Fspace of time."
