OL,6,FWhat are nitazenes?
OL,8,FNitazenes are synthetic opioids first
OL,9,Fdeveloped as painkillers in the 1950s
OL,10,Fbut never approved for medical use.
OL,12,FMostly imported from China, they are
OL,13,Fappearing more and more in street
OL,14,Fdrugs because the amount of opium
OL,15,Fcoming out of Afghanistan has reduced
OL,16,Fsince the Taliban resized power there
OL,17,Fin 2021.
