OL,3,CMum's warning over super-strength drug
OL,4,Cwhich killed her son
OL,6,FNitazenes are a cheap, highly
OL,7,Faddictive way for drug dealers to bulk
OL,8,Fout their product - but they can be
OL,9,Fdeadly even in tiny doses.
OL,11,FMany of those people who died had no
OL,12,Fidea they were taking them - they are
OL,13,Fbeing cut into other drugs like
OL,14,Fheroin, cocaine and even diazepam and
OL,15,Fxanex.
OL,17,FMany forms of nitazenes have now been
OL,18,Fcontrolled as Class A drugs by the
OL,19,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
