OL,3,CMum's warning over super-strength drug
OL,4,Cwhich killed her son
OL,6,FThey prompted the National Crime
OL,7,FAgency to warn that there's never been
OL,8,Fa more dangerous time to take drugs in
OL,9,Fthe UK.
OL,11,FSince Dylan's death in 2021,
OL,12,Ffatalities linked to nitazenes in the
OL,13,FUK have risen - in 2024, 195 deaths
OL,14,Fwere recorded, almost four times the
OL,15,Fnumber the year before.
OL,17,FClaire is now campaigning to raise
OL,18,Fawareness about the dangers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
