OL,6,FOne charity, Waythrough, has been
OL,7,Ftraining everyone from bin workers, to
OL,8,Fmagistrates, to bouncers.
OL,10,FNational harm reduction lead Jon
OL,11,FFindlay said: "It's really important
OL,12,Fthat more and more people carry
OL,13,Fnaloxone and know how to use naloxone
OL,14,Fto be able to just respond in case
OL,15,Fsomebody overdoses.
